{"tid":1844864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【1.29大三罷】小弟已經射左波，你呢？","createTime":"2020-01-26T21:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T04:45:10.000Z","uid":316614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c671d72f4becb849e7732d3c9102a0afc7b463","tid":1844864,"uid":316614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T21:02:33.000Z","msg":"小弟係一個手停口停d打工仔，之前幾次都罷過工，食少左幾餐，但係過到日子，無悔。<br />\n<br />\n大難臨頭，唔知講咩好。食少兩餐唔會中肺炎既，哈哈哈哈。如果真係咁唔好彩既話，我會做鬼搵返班黑警同支那狗算賬。<br />\n<br />\n我地走過左夏天同秋天，衣家捱埋個冬天就會春暖花開，我地一齊走落去啦好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"2a8f68ce3fa3ab1d19a3ddf09bf421796042fbca","tid":1844864,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T21:08:00.000Z","msg":"但要記住罷工唔係罷一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1d0e11956cf4b04b229e289aae0ef267205031","tid":1844864,"uid":316614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a8f68ce3fa3ab1d19a3ddf09bf421796042fbca","tid":1844864,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T21:08:00.000Z","msg":"但要記住罷工唔係罷一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"當然啦！"}]}